Description.LocalizedString: An item originating from Terra Primus and manifested by the Rift. Something about the structure depicted on it feels powerful and imposing.
An item originating from Terra Primus and manifested by the Rift. The third eye seems to imply deep-seeded knowledge or perhaps a psychic connection.
An item originating from Terra Primus and manifested by the Rift. There is something reassuring about the golden scarab upon it.
An item originating from Terra Primus and manifested by the Rift. The flower radiates with luminous light.
A symbol of winter, cold to the touch.
David enjoyed a good ol' fashioned dust-up, but when things got out of hand, the brass came out.
And the winner for outstanding information series is… Jane Romero!
A short-tempered brawler, David enjoyed starting his day with a pint and a punch-up.
A humble prize awarded after a string of exhausting battles.
Something dark in her family's past suffocates the bloodline.
A clever creature, one can't help but admire its ability to thrive in nearly any land.
Wishing longevity in a realm of terror and torture may be more akin to a curse.
So begins the cycle anew…
Without a magic hat, the snowman is fortunate enough to not have a soul to be beaten, worn, and broken.
A unique solution for those who want more murder in their Christmas holidays.
5, 4, 3… "I'm Jane Romero, and that is it for us today. We'll leave you with Corral Harp and a cut off her new album."
A charm for warding off evil, Kazan wore it when he left home to fulfill his destiny.
There's something striking about how blood contrasts against a snowy white sheet.
The Doctor rejected notions that his job was simple torture. This was science.
A light to guide your way into the new lunar cycle.
A lucky silk bag that carries good fortune.
There may be potential, but it's overgrown with doubt.
A watchful eye can see growth, slight as it may be.
The sprigs press forward with quiet confidence.
The branches expand upon the sturdy base.
The roots tear through the dirt, strangling all they encounter.
A powerful beast, spoiled on arrogance.
A powerful beast, relegated to the barren plains.
A powerful beast, saved from extinction.
A powerful beast, savage and bloody.
A powerful beast, loyal and respected.
Reminder of a time when the only thing hanging on hooks were Christmas ornaments.
